  <summary date="2021-01-06T14:55:30Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Heroes Small Business Lifeline Act

This bill provides economic support to small business affected by COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) by extending and expanding existing initiatives such as the Paycheck Protection Program, establishing a new lifeline grant program, and providing dedicated assistance for industries such as restaurants and live entertainment.</summary>
